      "name": "How much does HeyGen vs Synthesia cost?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "HeyGen plans start at $24/month (Creator), $49/month (Business), and custom Enterprise pricing. Synthesia starts at $22/month (Starter), $59/month (Creator), $99/month (Pro), and custom Enterprise plans. HeyGen offers better value for solo creators, while Synthesia's enterprise features justify its higher tiers."
